76條\r\n因過失致人於死者，處5年以下有期徒刑、拘役或50萬元以下罰\r\n金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/111%2c%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c510%2c20220428%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,111,交簡,510,20220428,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"交簡","JNO":"510","JDATE":"20220428","JTITLE":"過失致死"}